keywordDensity.businessDescription:
In the business for over twenty years, C & K Landscaping provides hard landscaping, driveways, block paving, paving contractors and surfacing within 50 miles of Trowbridge, Wiltshire.
We are have diggers from 1.5t to 3.5t and can haul away 5 ton of dig-out in one trip, saving costs to us which are passed on to the customer.

We have an excellent reputation with many dozens of satisfied customers, including some repeat ones who have moved to a new house and need more work done.

Patios, paths, driveways, moving earth around, building retaining walls, laying foundations, and these days even home/garden offices.
Everything that requires the skills of a builder or associated trades we can do.

Block paving, tarmacing, gravel, resin bound.
